            <title>[JDK-8307629] FunctionDescriptor::toMethodType should allow sequence layouts (mainline)</title>
                <link>https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8307629</link>
                <project id="10100" key="JDK">JDK</project>
                    <description>FunctionDescriptor::toMethodType should not be too opinionated on whether sequence layouts might sense or not as &amp;quot;by-value&amp;quot; parameters (even though the native linker does not support them).&lt;br/&gt;
